  "title": "Cashier",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for a friendly and detail-oriented Cashier to handle customer transactions efficiently while providing warm Thai-style hospitality. The role involves operating the POS system, handling cash/card payments, and supporting front-of-house operations during service hours.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong><br /><strong>- </strong>Greet customers politely and take orders accurately<br />- Operate POS system and process cash, NETS, and card payments to issue receipts and ensure correct change is given<br />- Coordinate with kitchen and service staff on orders<br />- Handle takeaway and delivery orders    <br />- Maintain cleanliness of cashier counter and front area  <br />- Balance cash drawer and prepare daily sales reports   <br />- Address basic customer inquiries and feedback professionally     <br />- Follow food safety, hygiene, and company SOPs<br /><strong></strong><br /><strong>Requirements</strong>    <br />- Minimum 1 year working experience in F&B sector<br />- Knowledge in handling POS system      <br />- Possess Food Safety Hygiene Certificate Level 1      <br />- Previous cashier or F&B experience preferred (training provided)<br />- Comfortable handling cash and electronic payments<br />- Basic English and Chinese required (Thai language is an advantage)<br />- Friendly, honest, and customer-oriented attitude who pays attention    to details and possess problem solving skills   <br />- Able to work shifts, weekends, and public holidays due to retail hours     <br />- Able to work well in a fast-paced restaurant environment<br /></p><p>Karen</p><p>1st Choice Recruit Pte Ltd</p><p>License No: 23C1844</p><p>Reg. No: R143661</p>",
